    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在<i>Horde Together</i>中抵御源源不断的僵尸和怪物浪潮，这是一款充满动作与混乱的合作生存游戏。和朋友们组队，搜寻装备，看看你能在末日世界中存活多久。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索不断变化的关卡，充满战利品、危险和不死生物的惊喜。在早期访问阶段，我们将定期推出新的地图和内容，让游戏保持新鲜和刺激。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>组建你的队伍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/043d008b23c43185ad1c19814e68be83.poster.avif?t=1747839324\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/043d008b23c43185ad1c19814e68be83.webm?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/043d008b23c43185ad1c19814e68be83.mp4?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有人能单独生存！和最多四个朋友组队，打造完美的怪物猎杀团队。<br>看着你的朋友被怪物压倒……然后尽量别犯同样的错误。<br>一起大笑、惊慌并尖叫！内建的语音聊天（基于距离）将很快上线。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与 Horde 作战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/dab1188724ab5d6a20f9c098893a8762.poster.avif?t=1747839324\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/dab1188724ab5d6a20f9c098893a8762.webm?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/dab1188724ab5d6a20f9c098893a8762.mp4?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建仅限朋友的私人大厅，或加入公共游戏，和陌生人组队。<br>在波次中复活倒下的队友……如果你足够勇敢的话。<br>生存是残酷的，快速的，并且可以无尽地重复挑战。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>终极军火库</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个地图中寻找武器、弹药和升级物品。<br>发现隐藏在每个关卡中的稀有物品和秘密。<br>在每波之间升级你的武器，以应对更强大的威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新的地图、敌人和装备将在早期访问阶段定期添加。</p>",
